question.title: Failed to Resolve Dependency: org.webrtc:google-webrtc:1.0.32006 in Kotlin
question.body:
I'm trying to add the WebRTC library to my Android project, but I'm encountering an issue with resolving the dependency. Here's the relevant part of my build.gradle.kts file:

dependencies {
    implementation("org.webrtc:google-webrtc:1.0.32006")
}

repositories {
    google()
    mavenCentral()
    jcenter()
    maven { url = uri("https://jitpack.io") }
}

I tried the methods of a question that was asked previously on Stack Overflow, but it is not fixing.

I was expecting that this dependency would install
